OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 15 Jun to Mon 29 Jun
OL,6,FFine and dry across many areas at
OL,7,Ffirst with high pressure the dominate
OL,8,Fpattern across the UK. Winds will
OL,9,Fmostly be light with temperatures
OL,10,Fprobably above normal. Later, low
OL,11,Fpressure will probably begin to have
OL,12,Fmore of an influence, especially
OL,13,Facross the south where heavy showers
OL,14,Fand thunderstorms become more
OL,15,Fprobable. It may also become hot in
OL,16,Fparts of the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
